headline: Coinbase, BiT Global End Legal Fight Over WBTC Delisting
summary: BiT Global agreed to dismiss its lawsuit against Coinbase, with each party covering its own legal expenses.

headline: Coinbase CEO Warns Bitcoin Will 'Take Over As Reserve Currency' If US Fails To Get Debt Under Control
summary: Does Bitcoin have the potential to become the reserve currency of the world? This is an idea that core believers in the asset have toyed with for years. The reasoning is that disillusionment with the debt-driven fiat system will lead to a mass exodus ...

headline: Robinhood continues rally ahead of S&P 500 rebalance
summary: Shares of Robinhood (HOOD) are trading up again on Friday ahead of tonight’s S&P 500 rebalance, marking the sixth consecutive day of outperformance for the stock. Earlier this week, BofA had pointed out that it saw Robinhood as “a prime candidate” to join the S&P 500. This is not the first time a Wall Street firm has named Robinhood as a potential pick.
